{"tid":1202750,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[反恐討論]如何報告恐怖分子行蹤","createTime":"2019-06-11T10:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:38:43.000Z","uid":258602,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f6461781fbd9c08e8f355672ac96345485143acc","tid":1202750,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:21:46.000Z","msg":"E排香港咁動盪，恐怖主義又咁盛行，相信大家都驚有恐怖分子乘機搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁大家又有冇諗過假如遇上恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點樣有效報告佢地行蹤，令大眾提高警覺？<br />\n根據美軍野戰手冊 FM21-75 ( <a href=\"https://www.globalsecurity.org/military/library/policy/army/fm/21-75/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalsecurity.org%2Fmilitary%2Flibrary%2Fpolicy%2Farmy%2Ffm%2F21-75%2Findex.html&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=740c7ac2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.globalsecurity.org/military/library/policy/army/fm/21-75/index.html</a> ，E個網有好多美軍野戰手冊睇，等大家可以學多d野臨危不亂) Chapter 6，報告敵人行蹤時有一口訣：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">SALUTE</span></strong>(敬禮）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">S</span>ize:對方人數/規模<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>ctivity:對方做緊乜<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">L</span>ocation:對方喺咩位置<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">U</span>nit/Uniform:對方係邊支部隊，如果係恐怖分子分唔出，就講佢哋著咩衫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">T</span>ime:幾時見到佢哋<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">E</span>quipment：對方有咩裝備/武器<br />\n例子:我係朝早八點<span style=\"color: red;\">(T)</span>見到有約10個<span style=\"color: red;\">(S)</span>著藍色裇衫<span style=\"color: red;\">(U)</span>的恐怖分子，攞住黑色木棍<span style=\"color: red;\">(E)</span>係軒尼詩道<span style=\"color: red;\">(L)</span>向東追打市民<span style=\"color: red;\">(A)</span>，大家小心！<br />\n只要做齊SALUTE，就可以準確咁報告恐怖分子行蹤！<br />\n就算唔敢同班恐怖分子面對面搏命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，只要你用眼用囗/手發出警告，一樣可以做到野避免人命傷亡！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n延伸閲讀：[url]<a href=\"http://www.acewings.com/cobrachen/forum/topic.asp?TOPIC_ID=8700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.acewings.com%2Fcobrachen%2Fforum%2Ftopic.asp%3FTOPIC_ID%3D8700&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=faff91d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.acewings.com/cobrachen/forum/topic.asp?TOPIC_ID=8700</a><br />\n[/url] <br />\n台灣急救/防災討論post<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.acewings.com/cobrachen/forum/topic.asp?TOPIC_ID=10845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.acewings.com%2Fcobrachen%2Fforum%2Ftopic.asp%3FTOPIC_ID%3D10845&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=fe4bbd27\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.acewings.com/cobrachen/forum/topic.asp?TOPIC_ID=10845</a><br />\n台灣家居自衛討論post，真係唔好彩要同恐怖分子面對面搏命時可能有用<br />\n巴絲們有冇咩反恐小貼士，歡迎齊齊討論！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415b8905a5d486b56660adbf34f25958c736f264","tid":1202750,"uid":87116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:22:12.000Z","msg":"召集海外巴絲支援義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1202730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1202730</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f85a7c8e28efd7414294417eac3c46ab6296c894","tid":1202750,"uid":258602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"仲有唔記得講，記得唔好亂發訊息，以免亂上加亂"},{"pid":"6529861298637966b44596f001c2c220cee9989b","tid":1202750,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:17:39.000Z","msg":"制止恐怖分子，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc746af1059adedc20684009978b47ff6d8d54f","tid":1202750,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9304874d8e9e671e1151e1e13aca1bbd0363ade3","tid":1202750,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"記得e件事人人都可幫手<img src=\"/assets/